version = "0.1.0"

authors = ["Alexander Becker <abecker@bitflow.dev>"]

autoexamples = true
autotests = true

publish = true

prometheus = "0.12.0"
reqwest = "0.11.2"

warp = "0.3.1"

[dependencies.built]
version = "0.4.4"
features = ["git2", "chrono", "semver"]
optional = false

[dependencies.serde]

features = ["derive"]
optional = false

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.3.0"

version = "0.4.4"

oping = "0.4.0"
